If you want to make an attribute private but still intend to allow it to be set, then the commonly used idiom is to create a &quot;setter&quot;.
 
In this case, you need to do it twice, for each of your classes with private attributes that you nevertheless want to set.

```
class Student{
	public:
		void setroll(int newroll)
		{
